ebola data

Source: R/data.R
ebola.Rd

Person-time data for death from ebola. Data from https://datacompass.lshtm.ac.uk/599/ Marks, M. Learning Clinical Epidemiology with R. (Project). London School of Hygiene & Tropical Medicine, London, United Kingdom.

ebola

Format

A dataframe

id

Unique patient identifier

age

Age in years

age_group

Grouped age

sex

Sex

disease_onset

Date of onset (date class)

disease_ended

Date of death or recovery (date class)

days_at_risk

Number of days at risk of death

status

Died or recovered (string)

transmission

How ebola was transmitted

died

Integer 1 = died, 0 = survived
